{
  "doc_id": "50716",
  "text": "With the rapid development of nanotechnology, miniaturized structures with nanoscale features can be precisely designed, manufactured and applied in the so-called Nano-Electro-Mechanical Systems (NEMS) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Since, Carbon Nano Tubes (CNTs) and nonlocal elastic beams with nanoscale thickness (nanorod) have good electrical properties and high mechanical strength, they are most popular in NEMS [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Moreover, they are of significance for use in advanced catalysts, adsorbents, composite materials and ceramics [CITATION_5] .",
